msgstr ""
"When `@llm_chat(...)` uses tools with runtime (such as `PyRepl`), the "
"framework injects a deduplicated `Tool Best Practices` block at the top of "
"the prompt; runtime primitive guidance will be included in the tool's best "
"practices entries."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:326
msgid ""
"当 `PyRepl` 挂载了 `SelfReference` 后端时，`llm_chat` 可从 toolkit 的 runtime backend "
"自动解析（无需强制传 `self_reference=`），同时仍支持显式传入 `self_reference=`。"
msgstr ""
"When `PyRepl` mounts the `SelfReference` backend, `llm_chat` can be "
"automatically resolved from the toolkit's runtime backend (no need to "
"forcibly pass `self_reference=`), while still supporting explicitly passing "
"`self_reference=`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:328
msgid ""
"首次回合安全：若 memory key 为空，会在执行工具前把当前 system prompt 写入 `self_reference`，确保 "
"runtime 读取不为空且包含 system 消息。"
msgstr ""
"First round safety: If the memory key is empty, the current system prompt "
"will be written to `self_reference` before tool execution, ensuring that the"
" runtime reads a non-empty value containing the system message."

