msgid "无依赖的任务尽量并行 `fork.spawn(...)`。"
msgstr ""
"Tasks without dependencies should be parallelized as much as possible using "
"`fork.spawn(...)`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:408
msgid "fork 前先整理记忆：弱相关信息先总结或落盘。"
msgstr ""
"Before forking, organize memory first: summarize or persist weak related "
"information first."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:409
msgid "fork 提示词写清完成边界和验收标准，优先文件+回传消息交接。"
msgstr ""
"Clearly state the completion boundaries and acceptance criteria in the fork "
"prompt, prioritizing file + return message handover."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:410
msgid "fork 结果默认是紧凑模式；需要子历史时再按需 `include_history=True`。"
msgstr ""
"The fork result is in compact mode by default; when you need child history, "
"set `include_history=True` on demand."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:411
msgid "每个里程碑后回收并整理记忆，再进入下一阶段。"
msgstr ""
"After each milestone, retrieve and organize memories, then enter the next "
"phase."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:413
msgid "忘记记忆的注意事项："
msgstr "Notes on forgetting memory:"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:415
msgid "忘记记忆 **不是** `reset_repl`。"
msgstr "Forget memory **is not** `reset_repl`."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:416
msgid "`reset_repl` 仅清理 REPL 命名空间中的 Python 变量。"
msgstr "`reset_repl` only cleans up Python variables in the REPL namespace."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:417
msgid ""
"需要清除记忆时，请使用 `runtime.selfref.history.delete(...)` 或 "
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(...)`；`runtime.selfref.history.clear(...)` "
"会保留当前 system prompt。"
msgstr ""
"When you need to clear the memory, please use "
"`runtime.selfref.history.delete(...)` or "
"`runtime.selfref.history.replace(...)`; `runtime.selfref.history.clear(...)`"
" will retain the current system prompt."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:419
msgid ""
"所有操作都会写入 `SelfReference` 的内部存储，而不是直接暴露原始列表。单次对话中的记忆变更会在回合结束时合并进返回的 "
"`updated_history`（事件模式下为 `ReactEndEvent.final_messages`）。"
msgstr ""
"All operations are written to the internal storage of `SelfReference`, "
"rather than directly exposing the original list. Memory changes in a single "
"conversation will be merged into the returned `updated_history` at the end "
"of the turn (in event mode, it's `ReactEndEvent.final_messages`)."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:421
msgid "单个 REPL 中多 agent 共享"
msgstr "Multi-agent sharing in a single REPL"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:423
msgid "为不同 agent 使用不同的 `self_reference_key`："
msgstr "Use different `self_reference_key` for different agents:"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:435
msgid "这样可以为每个 agent 提供隔离的记忆空间。"
msgstr "This can provide each agent with an isolated memory space."

