msgstr "Audit file: `executions.jsonl`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:479
msgid "每条记录包含：执行时间、代码、执行结果、结构化错误详情、超时配置等。"
msgstr ""
"Each record contains: execution time, code, execution result, structured "
"error details, timeout configuration, etc."

